Megatron Revived/ Organics:
 
Organics took Windlord's hand and gave it a squeeze.  She gave him a sweet smile, and that also had Megatron's attention.  He began to leer down on the Maximal like the protective older step brother he used to be.
"I can't say," he said in response to Windlord's question,"I just hope he doesn't make a rash decision."
He started to step closer to Windlord, his left arm winding up for a punch in the shoulder.  Organics caught him and leaned back behind Windlord to shoot Megatron a nasty look.  Megatron dropped his arm and just walked, keeping an eye on Organics and Windlord.
